      "message": "I did this work before realizing that CCPR seems to be on its way out. In any case most individual miter-clip joins will be miter joins so it\u0027s sensible to support them directly if authors start preferring miter-clip.",
      "revId": "e3a38dc6a68d4e17dd926360802e00bfb8278d01",
